Hi

MAP information

This map is set in a grungy new york city subway. The map is optimised for 6vs6 or 8vs8.
This release is a beta, I decided to go for beta instead of alpha because I feel that there are not that may bugs for it to be at a alpha release ect. There could be bugs/glitches/exploits so if possible if you find any post them here so that I can fix them.

This is a gungame map/deathmap map. 

Most of all I hope you enjoy playing on my map, And if you could, please give feedback.

Thank you
